To be liked & loved while on your peak is normal,
but to be loved & supported through all the seasons is beyond blessed. ❤️

Maraming salamat sa lahat ng nagmamahal at patuloy na sumusuporta mula noon hanggang ngayon. 🙏🏻🥹 

#RAD
#volleyball #Sports 
#athlete #fblifestyle
